<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Order Cancellation Notice</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= @user.email %>,</p>
    
    <p>Your order #<%= @order.id %> has been cancelled.</p>

    <% if @order.refund_amount %>
      <h2>Refund Information:</h2>
      <p>
        A refund of $<%= @order.refund_amount %> has been initiated to your original 
        payment method. Please allow 5-10 business days for the refund to appear 
        on your statement.
      </p>
    <% end %>

    <h2>Cancelled Order Details:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Order Total: $<%= @order.total_price %></li>
      <li>Cancellation Date: <%= @order.updated_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
      <% if @order.notes.present? %>
        <li>Cancellation Reason: <%= @order.notes %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>

    <p>
      If you have any questions about this cancellation, please don't hesitate 
      to contact our customer service team.
    </p>

    <p>We hope to serve you again in the future.</p>
  </body>
</html> 